In order for the frosting to hold it's shape you need to use Manufacturing Cream (40% butterfat), that or add a bunch of stabilizers (yuck!). If you live in the Western states you can buy it at either Smart & Final or Cash & Carry stores (www.smartandfinal.com). The website will tell you where there is a store in your area. You can't buy it at just a regular grocery store, unfortunately.

